    public abstract class UdpProtocol
extends java.lang.Object
implements NettyBootstrap<io.netty.bootstrap.Bootstrap>
    Bootstrap (UDP) must use Bootstrap .

    The AbstractBootstrap.bind() methods are useful in combination with connectionless transports such as datagram (UDP). For regular TCP connections, please use the provided Bootstrap.connect() methods.

    从以下版本开始:
